<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>
        Manage robots
    </title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mw-540 p-3">
        <h3 class="mt-4">ü§ñ Telepresence Robot Portal</h3>
        <h5 class="py-2">Admin dashboard</h5>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid bg-dark">
        <div class="container mw-540 px-3 py-2">
            <div class=" d-flex align-items-center">
                <img src="/photos/<%= id %>.png" class="rounded-circle me-2" alt="" width="42" height="42">
                <div class="d-flex py-2 me-auto">
                    <h6 class="my-auto text-white"><b><%= name %></b><br>üèõÔ∏è <%= inst %></h6>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex py-2">
                    <form method="GET" action="/admin-dashboard">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">‚¨ÖÔ∏è Back</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mw-540 p-3">
        <h6 class="mt-2 mb-4"><b>Activate new robot</b></h6>
        <p><b>1. </b>Join the same WiFi network as the <i>Double 3</i>.</p>
        <p><b>2. </b>Open the Developer Monitor by navigating to <b>[DOUBLE_IP]:8080</b> using a web browser.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary"><i>Hint: you can find the <i>Double 3</i>'s IP address by tapping the WiFi
                icon on the robot.</i></p>
        <p><b>3. </b>Navigate to <b>API</b> via the toolbar, then enter and <b>Send</b> the following instruction under
            <b>Send Command Manually</b>.</p>

        <h6 class="ms-3">Command</h6>
        <div id="code-snippet" class="ms-3 me-5">api.setConfig</div>

        <h6 class="ms-3">Parameters (JSON object)</h6>
        <div id="code-snippet" class="ms-3 me-5">
            {<br>
            "key": "STANDBY_URL",<br>
            "value": "https://open-all-senses.cobotmakerspace.org/robot/a31e1e24-5449-4097-a015-52dea9d5a769"<br>
            }
        </div>

        <p><b>4. </b>Select <b>Reboot Head</b> via the power icon dropdown in the top right.</p>
        <p><b>5. </b>When <b class="text-primary">ü§ñ Fizz</b> appears on the <i>Double 3</i>'s screen, click the button
            below to finalise the connection.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>